{"tid":809754,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"新田購物城淪「死城」　城規會仍允續期多3年","createTime":"2018-09-07T12:00:20.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-07T13:23:44.000Z","uid":39464,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"ed2f2d2aa4059e37a571ec9f00d8eb3ed4deb81b","tid":809754,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-07T12:00:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180907/photo/bkn-20180907094135404-0907_00822_001_01p.jpg?20180907185230\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180907%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20180907094135404-0907_00822_001_01p.jpg%3F20180907185230&h=0f47a6a5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n新田購物城淪為死城，仍獲城市規劃委員會續期3年，立法會議員黃定光承諾會加強招商和宣傳，相信到時商戶有信心承租，購物城經營情況會改善。 <br />\n<br />\n城規會今(7日)午開會，委員認同規劃署，認為可以容忍續期多3年，因購物城聲稱可以滿足邊境旅客需要，亦無對周圍環境構成不協調。規劃署認為，購物城續期至2021年，要滿足多項要求，包括晚上11時至翌日早上8時不能營業，在渠務、水務及消防等亦要符合規定。 <br />\n<br />\n黃定光今早在電台節目稱，購物城租戶少，「十室九空都未達到」，216個舖位只得8至10間開業。他指現有的規劃許可在2015年獲批，清拆和構建用了兩年多時間，去年11月才得到入伙紙，到今年初才正式開業，招租時商家見租約期只剩約半年時間營運，認為投資有風險，不夠膽入場。<br />\n<br />\n他又說，交通方面，與「跨境全日通」有默契，購物城來往福田口岸，可以開達100班跨境旅遊巴，但因為無乘客，現時只開8班車，客量仍然很少。 <br />\n<br />\n鄰近落馬洲口岸的新田購物城佔地42萬平方呎，提供200多個舖位，造價達1.5億港元。其所在地於2015年9月獲城規會批准改劃用途，爲期3年，將於本月中到期。設立邊境購物城的原意為分流内地旅客，減輕北區居民的壓力，惟籌備工作拖拖拉拉近3年，購物城方於今年2月開始試業，亦只有10%商舖參與，試業期間場内已人流稀少「拍烏蠅」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180907/bkn-20180907094135404-0907_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180907%2Fbkn-20180907094135404-0907_00822_001.html&d=EAXJ%2Fs%2BQrGjAWLZqT%2Ff6zP%2F4Bxi6eTjWtF%2F0WJNXpvw%3D&h=0864d479\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180907/bkn-20180907094135404-0907_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"e4227cdecfac42e2e3bcf59db4a8faedd8932d60","tid":809754,"uid":29080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-07T12:33:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"546bd6f36b22c7634e4a8a88e4feffa6f831638a","tid":809754,"uid":54264,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-07T12:37:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://encrypted-tbn0.gstatic.com/images?q=tbn:ANd9GcSoEq1jH19rsSvPnp33oS4loL92Riqn7SwL1IRXubn9HjyiRwdc\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fencrypted-tbn0.gstatic.com%2Fimages%3Fq%3Dtbn%3AANd9GcSoEq1jH19rsSvPnp33oS4loL92Riqn7SwL1IRXubn9HjyiRwdc&h=e18eed11&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"62e7037ebd09b185ee8cbd8f135109db192e8516","tid":809754,"uid":56900,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-07T12:39:19.000Z","msg":"唔續咪盞d人流又去返晒元朗屯門<br />\n已經開始去返已經"},{"pid":"cf4022290ee6c69d43f29a369fdb0644a5afb9fb","tid":809754,"uid":65530,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-07T12:39:57.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"9bc357627184eb76b555575fcf712e7f12cf643f","tid":809754,"uid":10703,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"62e7037ebd09b185ee8cbd8f135109db192e8516","tid":809754,"uid":56900,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-07T12:39:19.000Z","msg":"唔續咪盞d人流又去返晒元朗屯門<br />\n已經開始去返已經"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-07T12:41:26.000Z","msg":"得小貓幾隻，點分流<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fb2d04d3d5eac6c3068449992af3b23e570de24f","tid":809754,"uid":147376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-07T12:45:28.000Z","msg":"[url]城規會明日討論新田購物城用地續期申請 <a href=\"http://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=319333&amp;refer=share[/url]\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D319333%26refer%3Dshare%5B%2Furl%5D&d=EAXJ%2Fs%2BQrGjAWLZqT%2Ff6zP%2F4Bxi6eTjWtF%2F0WJNXpvw%3D&h=eb8ef386\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D319333%26refer%3Dshare%5B%2Furl%5D&h=9704362e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://news.now.com/home/local/p